{"tid":2220957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯黃定光批抗疫基金3.0粗疏斥「仆街」 張建宗被罵感謝「語重心長」","createTime":"2020-09-28T04:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T05:08:23.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a055176a292dbb745c172aa2e6c66d0b55189996","tid":2220957,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eOGkI3MeJqSsqeGzLNBQugFxWyA=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JJWBALOV5CVJBELREJYU6ETBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeOGkI3MeJqSsqeGzLNBQugFxWyA%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JJWBALOV5CVJBELREJYU6ETBU.jpg&h=755c3f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張建宗順利進入會議廳時向記者揮手。本報記者攝<br />\n...<br />\n立法會財委會今早續審議涉款240億的「抗疫基金3.0」撥款，預料最快今晚表決。民建聯多名議員會上一邊聲稱不滿「抗疫基金3.0」內容，一邊表明會投票支持通過，黃定光更在會上公然「爆粗」，指政府聲稱要聘用很多人手才能找出需要受助的人時直指：「如果我公司係咁，仆街啦真係」；與會的政務司司長張建宗稱多謝黃「語重心長」，並稱會「鞭策自己做好啲」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/O3KD5IFJEBDM5GQPUGZOSD5KUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FO3KD5IFJEBDM5GQPUGZOSD5KUQ%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUj8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=327765bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200928%2FO3KD5IFJEBDM5GQPUGZOSD5KUQ%2F&h=aa89a102\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200928/O3KD5IFJEBDM5GQPUGZOSD5KUQ/</a>"},{"pid":"311fc81c179c430aa7513f8f1943656350210111","tid":2220957,"uid":49776,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"批評政策算唔算反政府反中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9e7d7f843a9b6fd22b5358cb1f5e96df78835d","tid":2220957,"uid":255637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-2